### 1. 회원가입 테스트
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolEmail": "aaaa",
  "password": "aaaa",
  "nickname": "df"
}


### 2. 로그인 테스트
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolEmail": "aaaa",
  "password": "aaaa"
}